Electricity is SO great. 

Ran the dishwasher. Did the kids laundry. Vacuumed. Washed our dog in warm water (we have on demand hot water so cold showers the while). Vacuumed again. Went shopping for eggs and milk. 

Now reading with good light as night falls and the moon rises.
